{"tid":2498552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"少年刑毀「喜茶」改判入更生中心 上訴庭今頒判詞指「裝修」與私了無異 須從嚴處理","createTime":"2021-04-21T08:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T11:47:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f625d825f94cd2a7319676ddcb4ee19128c356","tid":2498552,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:53:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=135101&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D135101%26currpage%3DT&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dGZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=a9d4f835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=135101&amp;currpage=T</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/12/%E6%BD%98%E5%85%86%E5%88%9D-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E5%BA%AD-%E5%BD%AD%E5%81%89%E6%98%8C-20201203224950_14cc_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F12%2F%25E6%25BD%2598%25E5%2585%2586%25E5%2588%259D-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%25BA%25AD-%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%2581%2589%25E6%2598%258C-20201203224950_14cc_large.jpg&h=efa9a83e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年5月13日全港多區舉行「和你Sing」活動「慶祝」特首林鄭月娥生日。現年17歲的少年在沙田新城市廣場的內地連鎖茶飲店「喜茶」以石頭損壞兩部收銀機顯示屏和一部八達通處理器，總值1萬5200元，當時有人在店外指揮及把風，企圖阻止商場保安進店。周早前承認一項刑事毀壞罪，被判處200小時社會服務令。上訴庭早前裁定原有判刑明顯不足，認為原審裁判官排除拘禁式刑罰屬原則性犯錯，終改判周入更生中心。上訴庭今頒下判詞指案件屬有預謀和計劃周詳，而犯罪者遮蓋容貌，而原審裁判官沒有明確指出及處理；亦沒有辨識本案與反修例運動相關的背景，強調讓「青少年罪犯」改過自新，認為此做法不當。<br />\n<br />\n高等法院首席法官潘兆初、上訴法庭法官彭偉昌及原訟法庭法官潘敏琦在判詞中指，本案屬有預謀和計劃周詳，除破壞茶飲店亦包括阻礙保安員，而犯案者遮蓋容貌，事後難以追查，而原審裁判官沒有明確指出及處理。他強調讓「青少年罪犯」改過自新的重要，非一般做法。而判刑當日被告差一日便滿17歲，法庭把他等同為16歲以下的少年犯處理並不合適。<br />\n<br />\n另外，判詞表示原審裁判官沒有明確辨認本案的反修例運動背景，案發地點為出事熱點，警員證人在展開拘捕行動後被圍堵及襲擊，法庭都不能漠視相關背景，加重本案嚴重性。<br />\n<br />\n此外，判詞亦指案中此類坊間俗稱為「裝修」的行為，其實就是對不同背景或立場的人肆意攻擊，帶有仇視及霸凌等效果，與「私了」無異，行為惡劣及對社會造成破壞，法庭須從嚴處理。<br />\n<br />\n綜合以上情況，判詞指被告應被處以拘禁式的刑罰，但考慮到他的年紀、態度、身體情況和造成的破壞有限等，故判以更生中心。"},{"pid":"79291ccdc105b20689703ef390eccc54a1c2efd4","tid":2498552,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a4faae6ca988c3d0ef55a1ae8aa594478bc7e6","tid":2498552,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"da796a2d1b7f46405c6777f3c5483feca1869b61","tid":2498552,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"又係呢3條狗官<br />\n收共產黨唔少錢啦"},{"pid":"9c97493cf066068799578940b15d605cf520fecd","tid":2498552,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"呢班官應該要享受吓大灣區嘅榮耀"},{"pid":"89467ed737a1ae463ffb8db58f5b02f678f20ee9","tid":2498552,"uid":82938,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"無暴力又話有遊行有演變成暴力風險"},{"pid":"edcfae7466a3594ab584c2fb2889c37945e27f45","tid":2498552,"uid":65790,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89467ed737a1ae463ffb8db58f5b02f678f20ee9","tid":2498552,"uid":82938,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"無暴力又話有遊行有演變成暴力風險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:57:59.000Z","msg":"全部都有佢講架遮<br />\n成班奶共咪認囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da6e98cb1de596ef4af2c61e09ca24a7b7bf944","tid":2498552,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c97493cf066068799578940b15d605cf520fecd","tid":2498552,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"呢班官應該要享受吓大灣區嘅榮耀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce93b625311362bc74885e03971507f32ff10863","tid":2498552,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edcfae7466a3594ab584c2fb2889c37945e27f45","tid":2498552,"uid":65790,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89467ed737a1ae463ffb8db58f5b02f678f20ee9","tid":2498552,"uid":82938,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"無暴力又話有遊行有演變成暴力風險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:57:59.000Z","msg":"全部都有佢講架遮<br />\n成班奶共咪認囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"無政治考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b258595901871c25648609f7920abfcacdd4ed5b","tid":2498552,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:07:13.000Z","msg":"揸𠝹刀桶人就高尚情操<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c924142fe1ed7927d17821b92917ff2f99b7c9","tid":2498552,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7220fb65ba97f7b088f9e654c6a5c9bedff9af89","tid":2498552,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:11:48.000Z","msg":"721咪又係私了"},{"pid":"1f469db7a316acfcd92dc6c50955edff25a7a908","tid":2498552,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef65d4fc339d287c90c0c713f11f5a2c5269f062","tid":2498552,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"狗官"},{"pid":"a240633dff3cb6f01b16185d4d3094752d08c71a","tid":2498552,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"28.  無論如何，答辯人僅為一名中五生，案發前從沒有工作經驗，對時政有偏激看法及曾在家人不知情下參與大型示威活動[26]，<span class=\"red\">所以未必能符合有關社會服務令的先決條件。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb783fc9fda6dc06437f51617d8ee57ae958288","tid":2498552,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:43:10.000Z","msg":"30.  於判處答辯人後一兩個月，在兩次處理同案第二被告的程序當中，原審裁判官承認「事後有重新審視過啲證據」，認為自己判罰答辯人時「未必有全面考慮例如案件組織性等等」。<span class=\"red\">他表明，上級法院的新近案例對他有約束力，著第二被告不要心存「無謂嘅幻想」[28]。最後第二被告被判入更生中心。<strong><ins>也就是說，連原審裁判官本身都意識到判罰社會服務令有錯。</ins></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792d3ac4bcee1095d3cdd68db3283c45ee1da67c","tid":2498552,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:44:07.000Z","msg":"例如，及至判刑當天，<span class=\"red\">答辯人還差一日便滿十七歲，法庭一般不會形容為「非常年輕」</span>[31]，若然把他等同為少年犯（16歲以下）就更不合適。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcc0a9dca445a87fe94f0ef0851d3cad2452eb3","tid":2498552,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:44:09.000Z","msg":"呢3隻仲狗撚過裁判官"},{"pid":"6fe2f2bc79ab910b6e3a7a540c49099d37b971a2","tid":2498552,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:46:05.000Z","msg":"I. 合適的替代判刑<br />\n<br />\n47.  由本庭下令索取的首輪報告指答辯人有哮喘和體能未能達到勞教中心的要求。同時，報告引述答辯人自我介紹時只提到他在校際朗誦比賽中獲獎而對他在賽跑和足球運動上取得的佳績隻字未提。本庭問吳大律師何以會這樣，得到的回覆是報告撰寫人沒問，<span class=\"red\">所以答辯人沒說，和哮喘確實從小便有及因疫情太長不能運動以致身體便差等模棱兩可的答案。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"blue\">無論如何，在本庭的要求下，懲教署在第二輪的報告確認，答辯人的體能確實未能達標，不宜被拘禁於勞教中心。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至於他據稱患有哮喘，最新的私人醫生報告亦證實，答辯人確有此病，雖然在2016年2月以後就再沒求醫。據他母親解釋就是運動和踢球令病情得以改善，但在疫情之下情況又逐漸轉差。<br />\n<br />\n48.  考慮到與案有關的一切情況，答辯人毫無疑問應該被處以拘禁式的刑罰。若然他的身體許可，<span class=\"red\">勞教中心會是最合適的選項。但基於現實，及考慮到他的年紀、現時態度和犯案時造成的實質破壞有限等因素，本庭認為更生中心<span class=\"xx-large\">尚</span>為一個可以接受的判刑。</span><br />\n<br />\nJ. 命令<br />\n<br />\n49.  本庭批准申請人的刑期覆核申請，撤銷原有的社會服務令，並下令把答辯人拘禁於更生中心。"},{"pid":"6fc855d9d45bf7fd406e3e778205fb36e9b65190","tid":2498552,"uid":92448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:59:53.000Z","msg":"支那曱甴集團"},{"pid":"043460903b118a736de8b92c87c81cc67a74333d","tid":2498552,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:07:40.000Z","msg":"司法迫害"},{"pid":"de0f333b91f1cd0645399e3662e0d94455a9a9a7","tid":2498552,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acb783fc9fda6dc06437f51617d8ee57ae958288","tid":2498552,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:43:10.000Z","msg":"30.  於判處答辯人後一兩個月，在兩次處理同案第二被告的程序當中，原審裁判官承認「事後有重新審視過啲證據」，認為自己判罰答辯人時「未必有全面考慮例如案件組織性等等」。<span class=\"red\">他表明，上級法院的新近案例對他有約束力，著第二被告不要心存「無謂嘅幻想」[28]。最後第二被告被判入更生中心。<strong><ins>也就是說，連原審裁判官本身都意識到判罰社會服務令有錯。</ins></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:35:38.000Z","msg":"溫咪講左好多次, 因為加刑庭指示先唔可以咁判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb31ba63bd649b19cd60a9b77d34b037536f14e","tid":2498552,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"加刑庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400e35ca7002b2606edb5a3bcf20c2b37aa1bfbc","tid":2498552,"uid":28938,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:52:49.000Z","msg":"坐完出黎好好做人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db867d608373e6052b244d5f0b186287f1e99051","tid":2498552,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"潘兆初<br />\n彭偉昌<br />\n潘敏琦<br />\n狗官食屎la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}